>jd: ?CINNRY A5 ICY +22 348
#note I was low on time and hadn't spotted what was coming next (ENCODE). quackle claims that NODE wins. but it is wrong because the actual right sequence takes a lot of moves. I can't say that ICY is really better than the alternatives but it's what I saw at the time. I think ICY loses by 6 and NODE loses by 7 if we both play optimally from here on out.
>Odette_Rio: CEGINS E9 ENC... +18 350
